methods.name: public Builder setStatus(@Nullable SafetySourceStatus status)
methods.comment: Sets data for the {@link SafetySourceStatus} to be shown in UI.

methods.name: public Builder addIssue(@NonNull SafetySourceIssue safetySourceIssue)
methods.comment: Adds data for a {@link SafetySourceIssue} to be shown in UI.

methods.name: public Builder setExtras(@NonNull Bundle extras)
methods.comment:
* Sets additional information for the {@link SafetySourceData}. * *

If not set, the default value is {@link Bundle#EMPTY}.

methods.name: public Builder clearExtras()
methods.comment:
* Resets additional information for the {@link SafetySourceData} to the default value of
         * {@link Bundle#EMPTY}.

methods.name: public Builder clearIssues()
methods.comment:
* Clears data for all the {@link SafetySourceIssue}s that were added to this {@link
         * Builder}.

methods.name: public SafetySourceData build()
methods.comment: Creates the {@link SafetySourceData} defined by this {@link Builder}.
